author: Emma Grey Ellis
title: Coronavirus Dreams Are Taking Over the Internet
description: The Covid-19 pandemic is causing some truly bizarre, and horrifying, night visions. Sharing them helps.
content: A California woman in her seventies was dreaming of a grocery store. Her cat had instructed her to buy a specific brand of chicken, but it was too expensive. When she got to the register with her cheaper chicken in tow, the cashier told the woman shed have to… [+6417 chars]
